item.title: Help with Cases
item.dc:creator: @jc22493 Jc22493
item.description:
@jc22493 wrote:

[quote=“wookiezz, post:10, topic:303245”]nope. Why should it be? can you like use it in the sense of how it would be?

Thanks,
Wookiezz[/quote]

Wrong.

case 100: // Random packet. case 50: // Do something. break; switch (variable) { case 51: // Do something. break; }

Correct.

case 100: // Random packet. switch (variable) { case 50: // Do something. break; case 51: // Do something. break; }
